Processing Layer

Measurement is not the end.
Between measurement and result there is processing.

Flow:

MERENJE
↓
OBRADA
↓
REZULTAT

OBRADA includes:

1. extraction of raw signal features
2. calculation of V_pre
3. calculation of V_post
4. calculation of ΔV
5. generation of device_signature
6. generation of sensor_pattern
7. generation of environment_pattern
8. writing to log

The processing layer connects the apparatus and the formula.
